          "answer": "समीकरण: 2x² - 7x + 3 = 0<br>सबसे पहले x² के गुणांक (2) से पूरे समीकरण को भाग दें:<br>=> x² - (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span>)x + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> = 0<br>=> x² - (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span>)x = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span><br>अब x के गुणांक (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span>) के आधे (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>) का वर्ग दोनों तरफ जोड़ने पर:<br>=> x² - (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span>)x + (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>)² = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> + (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>)²<br>बायां पक्ष (a - b)² के रूप में है:<br>=> (x - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>)² = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">49</span><span class=\"den\">16</span></span><br>=> (x - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>)² = (-24 + 49) / 16<br>=> (x - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>)² = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">25</span><span class=\"den\">16</span></span><br>दोनों तरफ वर्गमूल लेने पर:<br>=> x - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = ±<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">5</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span><br>स्थिति 1 (+ लेने पर):<br>x = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">5</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">12</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = 3<br>स्थिति 2 (- लेने पर):<br>x = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">5</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">2</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span><br>अतः समीकरण के मूल 3 और <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> हैं। Ans."
