          "answer": "<b>Step 1:</b> दिए गए मानों से समीकरण बनाना।<br>सूत्र: S_n = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">n</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + (n - 1)d]<br>S_7 = 49<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + (7 - 1)d] = 49<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">7</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + 6d] = 49<br>2a + 6d = (49 × 2) / 7<br>2a + 6d = 14<br>2 से भाग देने पर: a + 3d = 7 ---(समीकरण 1)<br><br>S_17 = 289<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">17</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + (17 - 1)d] = 289<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">17</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + 16d] = 289<br>2a + 16d = (289 × 2) / 17<br>2a + 16d = 34<br>2 से भाग देने पर: a + 8d = 17 ---(समीकरण 2)<br><br><b>Step 2:</b> समीकरणों को हल करना।<br>समीकरण (2) में से (1) घटाने पर:<br>(a + 8d) - (a + 3d) = 17 - 7<br>5d = 10<br>d = 2<br><br>d का मान समीकरण (1) में रखने पर:<br>a + 3(2) = 7<br>a + 6 = 7<br>a = 1<br><br><b>Step 3:</b> प्रथम n पदों का योग (S_n) ज्ञात करना।<br>यहाँ a = 1 और d = 2<br>S_n = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">n</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2a + (n - 1)d]<br>S_n = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">n</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2(1) + (n - 1)2]<br>S_n = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">n</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2 + 2n - 2]<br>S_n = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">n</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> [2n]<br>S_n = n × n = n²<br><br>Final Answer: अतः A.P. के प्रथम n पदों का योग n² होगा।"
