          "answer": "माना A.P. का प्रथम पद = a और सार्व अंतर = d<br>7वाँ पद (a_7) = a + 6d = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">9</span></span>   ...(i)<br>9वाँ पद (a_9) = a + 8d = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">7</span></span>   ...(ii)<br><br>समीकरण (ii) में से (i) को घटाने पर:<br>(a + 8d) - (a + 6d) = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">7</span></span> - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">9</span></span><br>=> 2d = (9 - 7) / 63<br>=> 2d = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">2</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span><br>=> d = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span><br><br>d का मान समीकरण (i) में रखने पर:<br>a + 6(<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span>) = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">9</span></span><br>=> a + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">6</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">9</span></span><br>=> a = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">9</span></span> - <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">6</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span><br>=> a = (7 - 6) / 63<br>=> a = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span><br><br>अब हमें 63वाँ पद (a_63) निकालना है:<br>a_63 = a + 62d<br>a_63 = (<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span>) + 62(<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span>)<br>a_63 = (1 + 62) / 63<br>a_63 = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">63</span><span class=\"den\">63</span></span> = 1.<br>अतः 63वाँ पद 1 है। Ans."
