        "answer": "<img src=\"images/math_ch9_iq_q3_tower_building_v2.png\" class=\"diagram-float educational-diagram\"><b>Step 1:</b> चरों को मानना।<br>माना भवन AB = h और मीनार CD = 50m है।<br>दूरी BD = x मीटर।<br><br><b>Step 2:</b> आधार की दूरी ज्ञात करना।<br>समकोण ΔCDB में: tan 60° = 50 / x<br>√3 = 50 / x  => x = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">50</span><span class=\"den\">√3</span></span> मीटर।<br><br><b>Step 3:</b> भवन की ऊँचाई (h) ज्ञात करना।<br>समकोण ΔABD में: tan 30° = h / x<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">√3</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">h</span><span class=\"den\">x</span></span>  => x = h√3<br><br><b>Step 4:</b> हल करना।<br>h√3 = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">50</span><span class=\"den\">√3</span></span>  => h = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">50</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> = 16.67 मीटर।<br><br><b>Final Answer:</b> अतः भवन की ऊँचाई 16.67 मीटर (या 16 <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">2</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> मीटर) है।"
